 premium between LDO perpetual and spot prices, with settlements occurring every 60 minutes. The platform's off-chain order book processes rate calculations efficiently while maintaining on-chain settlement transparency. Funding payments are automatically debited or credited to trader positions without requiring manual intervention. Aevo's rollup architecture enables faster funding rate updates compared to traditional Layer 1 implementations."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
